ng the power to become – and their effect of beholders as unforeseen, violent, and excessive – a violence of sensation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aPainting, BaroquexThemes, motiveszEurope. 0aViolence in art. 4aArt and Material Culture. 4aHistory, Art History, and Archaeology. 4aLiterary Theory, Criticism, and History. 7aART / History / Baroque & Rococo.2bisacsh  aBaroque, Violence, Painting, Materiality, Temporality, Narrative.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076709408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2022z9783110992809oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishz978311099281608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048543830?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048543830423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048543830/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076709-4  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099281-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DPKb2022